data.description: LOAN IS ASSUMABLE AT 2.9%. Sellers will give a $3K paint allowance with a full price offer.  This stunning home sits on a private cul de sac, boasting 1.3 acres of land and over $100,000 in upgrades within the past 2 years. And, there is room for your horses! The spacious 3 car garage easily accommodates trucks with receivers, while the new roof (with warranty) and freshly painted exterior enhance its curb appeal. Inside, the home features newer kitchen appliances & large pantry ensuring fewer trips to the store and plenty of storage.
